body:
Hi, Not really sure how to say this without sounding rude but here goes. I was on a 18 or so win streak in ranked and had climbed back up to silver 2 after being in b1 from placements. Now my issue is not that i was placed in bronze 1 at all. as you can see if you aren&#039;t meant to be in the division you will climb, but i just had my first loss and it was due to an unsettling circumstance. In my promo for silver 2 i was placed with somebody who had NEVER played ranked, i&#039;m not talking about &quot;had good mmr&quot; no just never played ranked. He proceeded to not understand how to gank or jungle and that&#039;s fine for a new player i get it but my question is why am i being placed with him? especially on an almost 20 game win streak in my promos? is that just bad matchmaking or is there something that i&#039;m missing?

Not meaning to come across rude just confused as to why we would be paired as it&#039;s just as unfair for that to be his first game as it is for him to be in my sil 2 promos.
Cheers :){{item:3070}} {{item:3070}} {{summoner:3}} {{sticker:zombie-nunu-bummed}}
